OL,3,CFirms 'may need to be forced to accept
OL,4,Ccash to prevent two-tier society'
OL,6,FBusinesses may need to be forced to
OL,7,Faccept coins and banknotes, to make
OL,8,Fsure the UK does not drift into a loss
OL,9,Fof cash acceptance for those who rely
OL,10,Fon it, the Treasury Committee has
OL,11,Fwarned.
OL,13,FThe committee said cash usage has
OL,14,Fdecreased significantly across the UK
OL,15,Fand it is urging the Government to
OL,16,Fundertake a "vastly improved"
OL,17,Fmonitoring and reporting of cash
OL,18,Facceptance levels.
