OL,3,CFirms 'may need to be forced to accept
OL,4,Ccash to prevent two-tier society'
OL,6,FThe report said: "There may come a
OL,7,Ftime in the future where it becomes
OL,8,Fnecessary for HM Treasury to mandate
OL,9,Fcash acceptance if appropriate
OL,10,Fsafeguards have not been implemented
OL,11,Ffor those who need physical cash, and
OL,12,Fthe level of cash acceptance begins to
OL,13,Flead to widespread detriment.
OL,15,F"To ensure that HM Treasury has the
OL,16,Finformation it needs to make this
OL,17,Fdecision, cash acceptance levels in
OL,18,Fthe UK must be monitored to ensure we
OL,19,Fdo not sleepwalk into a loss of cash
OL,20,Facceptance for those who need it.
