OL,6,FIn January, Economic secretary to the
OL,7,FTreasury Emma Reynolds told a Treasury
OL,8,FCommittee hearing: "We have no plans
OL,9,Fto regulate businesses to compel them
OL,10,Fto accept cash ` big or small."
OL,12,FWhen it was put to her that certain
OL,13,Fmarginalised people could be excluded,
OL,14,Fshe said: "I think our solution to
OL,15,Fthat, through the financial inclusion
OL,16,Fwork that we're doing, is to try to
OL,17,Ftackle digital exclusion."
