OL,6,FFollowing an IT failure at Barclays,
OL,7,Fthe committee wrote to major retail
OL,8,Fbanks in the UK to gather more
OL,9,Finformation on the frequency and
OL,10,Flength of IT failures.
OL,12,FThe letters received from banks
OL,13,Findicated at least 158 banking IT
OL,14,Foutages between January 2023 and
OL,15,FFebruary 2025.
OL,17,FIt also said the lack of consistent
OL,18,Fevidence makes it difficult for
OL,19,Fanyone, including the Treasury, to
OL,20,Fdetermine the state of cash acceptance
OL,21,Fin the UK.
