OL,6,FData from cash access and ATM network
OL,7,FLink in 2024 indicated that half of
OL,8,Fpeople had been somewhere that did not
OL,9,Faccept cash or discouraged cash usage
OL,10,Fin the previous eight weeks.
OL,12,FCommittee chairwoman Dame Meg Hillier
OL,13,Fsaid: "The Government is in the dark
OL,14,Fon how widely cash is being accepted
OL,15,Fand that is completely unsustainable.
OL,16,FWe are at risk of a two-tier society
OL,17,Fwhere the most vulnerable bear the
OL,18,Fbrunt and this needs to be a wake-up
OL,19,Fcall.
