OL,6,FUK Finance has highlighted a
OL,7,Fsignificant decline in the use of cash
OL,8,Fas a form of payment, the report said.
OL,9,FCash was used for 51% of all payments
OL,10,Fin 2013, but by 2023 this had fallen
OL,11,Fto 12%.
OL,13,FThe Financial Conduct Authority (FCA)
OL,14,Frequires banks and building societies
OL,15,Fdesignated by the Government to assess
OL,16,Fand fill gaps, or potential gaps in
OL,17,Fcash access provision that
OL,18,Fsignificantly impact consumers and
OL,19,Fbusinesses.
