OL,6,FThe access to cash regulations apply
OL,7,Fto 14 banks and building societies
OL,8,Fdesignated by the Treasury, with Link
OL,9,Fdesignated as scheme operator.
OL,11,FIf a gap in cash access services is
OL,12,Fidentified, additional services may
OL,13,Fneed to be provided, such as a banking
OL,14,Fhub or an ATM.
OL,16,FA milestone was recently reached in
OL,17,Fthe provision of banking hubs, with
OL,18,F150 having been opened.
