OL,6,FJohn Howells, chief executive of Link,
OL,7,Fsaid: "This timely report is further
OL,8,Fevidence that cash continues to be
OL,9,Fabsolutely critical. Critical for the
OL,10,Fmillions of people who rely on it day
OL,11,Fin, day out, and critical for national
OL,12,Fsecurity and resilience."
OL,14,FSam Smethers, chief executive of
OL,15,Fcharity Surviving Economic Abuse,
OL,16,Fsaid: "Abusers control survivors' bank
OL,17,Faccounts or prevent them from opening
OL,18,Fone to control and trap them. This
OL,19,Fforces many to secretly save cash or
OL,20,Fflee with only the clothes on their
OL,21,Fbacks and change in their pockets."
