OL,6,FA Treasury spokesperson said: "Cash
OL,7,Fcontinues to be used by millions of
OL,8,Fpeople across the UK and we are
OL,9,Fworking with the banks to roll out 350
OL,10,Fhubs by the end of this Parliament so
OL,11,Fthat people and businesses in areas
OL,12,Fthat have lost local bank branches
OL,13,Fstill have access to it.
OL,15,F"We welcome businesses who do want to
OL,16,Fcontinue accepting cash and new rules
OL,17,Fintroduced by the Financial Conduct
OL,18,FAuthority support this by helping them
OL,19,Fto make deposits."
